tasks.description:
pg_trgm GIN 인덱스를 활용한 ilike OR 쿼리로 제품명/브랜드 검색 엔드포인트를 구현한다. 공용 에러 헬퍼(lib/api/errors.ts), Zod 기반 검증(lib/api/validation.ts), 응답 DTO(types/api.ts)를 함께 구축한다.

엔드포인트: GET /api/products/search?q={query}
응답: { items: Array<{ id, name, brand, category, image_url }> } 최대 10건, oliveyoung_rank 오름차순

tasks.implementationGuide:
1. pnpm add zod
2. lib/api/errors.ts:
```ts
export type ApiErrorCode = 'INVALID_QUERY'|'INVALID_BODY'|'PRODUCT_NOT_FOUND'|'EMPTY_SLOT'|'DB_ERROR'|'INTERNAL';
export function jsonError(status: number, code: ApiErrorCode, message: string) {
  return Response.json({ error: { code, message } }, { status });
}
```
3. types/api.ts: ProductSearchItem, ProductSearchResponse 정의
4. lib/api/validation.ts: searchQuerySchema = z.object({ q: z.string().min(1).max(100).refine(s => !/[\u0000-\u001F]/.test(s)) })
5. app/api/products/search/route.ts:
```ts
export async function GET(req: NextRequest) {
  const parsed = searchQuerySchema.safeParse({ q: req.nextUrl.searchParams.get('q') });
  if (!parsed.success) return jsonError(400, 'INVALID_QUERY', ...);
  const safe = parsed.data.q.replace(/[%_,()]/g, ' ').trim();
  const supabase = await createClient();
  const { data, error } = await supabase.from('products')
    .select('id,name,brand,category,image_url')
    .or(`name.ilike.%${safe}%,brand.ilike.%${safe}%`)
    .order('oliveyoung_rank', { ascending: true, nullsFirst: false })
    .limit(10);
  if (error) return jsonError(500, 'DB_ERROR', 'DB 오류');
  return Response.json({ items: data });
}
```

